{"tid":1613734,"cid":16,"subCid":0,"title":"【光復Starbucks】其實亞洲區總部喺香港","createTime":"2019-10-02T15:20:30.000Z","updateTime":"2019-10-05T23:49:45.000Z","uid":70217,"like":46,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":15,"replies":[{"pid":"fc3136f70a2f8083f20bada9a58a884a6a0bd01e","tid":1613734,"uid":70217,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-02T15:20:30.000Z","msg":"AP（亞洲太平洋區域）係under Starbucks總公司<br />\n不屬於美心集團<br />\n員工咩國籍都有<br />\n根據我嘅經驗，每次AP巡舖啲分區/OM都會好緊張<br />\n相信對美心有一定監管作用<br />\n而美心係負責香港、澳門、新加坡同柬埔寨嘅Starbucks業務發展<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/Y15MeVW.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FY15MeVW.png&h=83a2a45a&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/P4N6ZnB.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FP4N6ZnB.png&h=804a9c74&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n不如大家brainstorm吓<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 唔知同佢哋講有冇用<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/j8LMeR1.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fj8LMeR1.png&h=210b8c88&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/photo.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"000992d1c627165c28bf253badfefe8de35e9578","tid":1613734,"uid":81996,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-02T15:21:21.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"562cf2bb560193e14f4846f12d59d08bc9b9c602","tid":1613734,"uid":4917,"like":9,"dislike":0,"score":9,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-10-02T15:23:56.000Z","msg":"啱啦，等佢收返美心個經營權"},{"pid":"dc2f2c37e76e3aacae947bfef9f5d44f4c25f336","tid":1613734,"uid":70217,"like":21,"dislike":0,"score":21,"quote":{"pid":"562cf2bb560193e14f4846f12d59d08bc9b9c602","tid":1613734,"uid":4917,"like":9,"dislike":0,"score":9,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-10-02T15:23:56.000Z","msg":"啱啦，等佢收返美心個經營權"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-02T15:31:02.000Z","msg":"講真好多partner走都係因為美心完全唔符合starbucks宗旨<br />\n人哋真係會將partner擺喺「公司財產」定義嘅第一位<br />\n供書教學，literally供埋partner讀大學<br />\n香港唔講到咁偉大